  "texts": [
    "39 AI-based CDSS have similarly demonstrated positive outcomes on prescribing safety and potential cost savings from DRP avoidance.",
    "40, 41 These trials underscore the vital role of CDSS in enhancing prescribing safety, whether through rule-based systems or advanced AI-driven analytics.",
    "However, the successful implementation and effectiveness of these systems depend on several factors, including system design, user interface, integration into clinical work ows, and training of healthcare professionals.",
    "LLM-based CDSS present with unique advantages such as the ability to process and interpret large volumes of unstructured clinical data, adapt to evolving medical knowledge, and provide personalized treatment recommendations.",
    "42, 43 This supports more informed, relevant and individualized patient care decisions."
  ]
